 degree required 3+ years' experience as a draftsman Exemplary knowledge of CAD Proficiency with Microsoft Excel Ability to follow safety rules Experience in commercial drafting Architect related job titles: Senior Draftsperson Draftsperson Residential Architect Commercial Draftsperson Commercial Architect Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
